 "name": "Customize the company_context block",
 "text": "Replace the bracketed placeholders with your company name, ICP, value prop, named customers with outcomes, pricing, pains, exclusions, sales stages, and the OneDrive/SharePoint paths to your CRM, pipeline workbook, and proposal template."
 },
 {
